## Development

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/vstorm-co/pydantic-deepagents.git
cd pydantic-deepagents

# Install dependencies
make install

# Run tests
make test

# Run all checks (lint, typecheck, test, coverage)
make all
```

